     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      ** Warning fields/message IDs/message data (arrays)
      ** from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    WFldNmXAr
